[29/06/2018 14:15:58] <font color="#ffff00">autora de libros de cocina,</font>
[29/06/2018 14:16:01] <font color="#ffff00">y Victoria Curry,</font>
[29/06/2018 14:16:01] <font color="#ffff00">su secretaria privada.</font>
