[29/06/2018 16:44:48] <font color="#00ff00">"Alex me ha invitado</font>
[29/06/2018 16:44:48] <font color="#00ff00">a recolectar musgo</font>
[29/06/2018 16:44:51] <font color="#00ff00">para reponer el suministro</font>
